data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled within the Sunrise gated community! This 2020 residence boasts timeless elegance and modern comforts. Spanning 1826 square feet, this abode offers a harmonious blend of functionality and style. Upon entry, you are greeted by a versatile flex space, ideal for a home office, library, or even a cozy sitting area. As you leave the foyer, you're embraced by an inviting open floor plan seamlessly connecting the kitchen and living room, perfect for effortless entertaining and daily living. The warmth of a gas fireplace adds an inviting ambiance, perfect for chilly evenings or cozy gatherings. Plantation shutters adorn every window, offering both privacy and a touch of sophistication throughout the home. Tray ceilings grace both the living room and Primary, elevating the aesthetic appeal. The Primary Suite is a haven of relaxation, featuring an ensuite Primary Bath with a double vanity, extra-large walk-in closet, separate water closet, and a spacious walk-in shower. From the living room, elegant French doors are your gateway to your screened-in porch, where mornings can be spent sipping coffee in tranquility or evenings enjoying the Florida breeze. Outside, a privacy-fenced backyard awaits, providing a serene retreat for outdoor activities. A Tuff Shed adds practical storage solutions, ensuring a clutter-free living environment. Right outside of the back gate of NAS Pensacola, this makes for a primely located home as you are mere miles from the white sands of Perdido Key Beach, as well as all the restaurants and stores you could hope for. Don’t miss out on the perfect Pensacola home!
